{"tid":140170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你站一下沒關係吧？老人霸佔對號座　卻從桃園搭到七堵","createTime":"2017-03-02T04:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T23:43:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8df4d3c397d2901bb18d43c7d5a91c65cb48d4af","tid":140170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:05:37.000Z","msg":"│TVBS新聞網<br />\n<img src=\"http://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2017/01/04/20170104224922-8efcaaa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F04%2F20170104224922-8efcaaa0.jpg&h=0356e99f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許多人再搭乘火車時，為了讓自己搭乘舒適，都會提前訂位確保自己能夠有位子坐，然而若你在上車時卻發現有長輩坐在自己的位子上，你會選擇怎麼做呢？一名網友日前搭火車時，目睹一名阿嬤沒買票卻堅持要人讓座，讓他傻眼直呼「叫你阿嬤不要亂搭自強號！」<br />\n<br />\n一名網友在社群平台Dcard發文表示，自己日前搭乘自強號北上時，旁邊坐著一名沒有購買座位的老奶奶，後來到達台北時，購買該座位的乘客走到老奶奶旁邊看著她，殊不知老奶奶卻向女乘客表示「讓我坐一下沒關係啊吧」，態度還很和善彷彿「一切都很合理」，甚至還指著另一名在桃園站讓座的女生，向該名購票的女乘客表示「剛剛那個妹妹讓座給我」，還不斷強調「她人很好」、「你站一下應該沒關係吧？」，結果這名老奶奶從原本的「只坐一下」，卻一路搭到「七堵」才下車，讓一旁的網友當場傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n而該名購票的女乘客在老奶奶下車後，立刻打電話給友人講述事發經過，口氣十分無奈，讓網友大嘆，許多人願意花錢購買自強號座位，都是為了讓旅途更快更舒服，但很多老人卻仗著自己年紀大，硬是將別人花錢購買的位子這樣坐走，男網友也強調「別人不強迫你就真的不起來，不就幸好飛機沒賣站票，不然你連別人的機位也坐走。」<br />\n<br />\n最後網友也呼籲大家，請跟自己的爺爺奶奶講清楚，如果真的很急就買對號票，沒有買的話就「站好站滿」，更說這種行為真的非常不禮貌，「請不要讓自己的家人成為這樣破壞別人舒服旅程的討厭鬼。」"},{"pid":"f9a13c356986addac204029be10d2587e1966477","tid":140170,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班死廢青就企喇屌<br />\n邊有資格坐低啊<br />\n我地啲老友記錢就比少份，位就冇少個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當臉屌呢啲廢老喇<br />\n我真係唔撚忍"},{"pid":"e675d4804c6d347c1608b2a80f28eef3a32a9606","tid":140170,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班死廢青就企喇屌<br />\n邊有資格坐低啊<br />\n我地啲老友記錢就比少份，位就冇少個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當臉屌呢啲廢老喇<br />\n我真係唔撚忍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前寶島咪試過有一單直情叫埋車長黎都冇用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db4e54f4371cb5a10611dcbc9ffb40580598e50","tid":140170,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:13:27.000Z","msg":"台仔渣ga"},{"pid":"a069cda409d5119f03b7054373a2cffd7d915a42","tid":140170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d25948b2262045178f96001012030c516ec986e","tid":140170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5ca87f7bab25f63d5257c116213b50daead614","tid":140170,"uid":61327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"咁都讓 on9台仔台妹"},{"pid":"e6e758596cc3d4f4617731628aec3911e0708a04","tid":140170,"uid":84465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"台灣人冇鬼用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e4244505484340e833e6f4f43cf64fded7d4de","tid":140170,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"1f14d745242cdef8229a8467084618135126ef3b","tid":140170,"uid":67256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92261450399ad35e45dc123a767ccf2c7e67991","tid":140170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a642da1f9c48fd80771dbc49662371fca6f551fe","tid":140170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c42f5ad3216f77c5e732cff4bf1d4290fef3fa","tid":140170,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"台灣d 左癌都好撚嚴重<br />\n試過去某d 得巴士到既景點，個巴士站已經排好晒d 坐位<br />\n你想有位坐就排隊，你企都無所謂既就等d 人坐晒先塞入去<br />\n有d 廢老又唔想排隊但又想坐，就等人坐晒先入去，然後叫坐關愛座讓俾佢，仲要d 語氣好老撚馮咁，坐緊既好撚唔服氣，但又唔敢出聲，又真係讓俾佢<br />\n明明排坐位條隊都唔使排好耐，而且可以坐住等，d 廢老都可以咁蠻不講理"},{"pid":"2f4fea9f46be128e252e1b87043729c9f7d4e4b8","tid":140170,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"其實老人搭飛機有無得免費Upgrade頭等?"},{"pid":"6449d46a87a372fc340d3e4e2698f1d6f463d068","tid":140170,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"最美的風景"},{"pid":"ef93ea615b4fae45fa7d3689b8ef90bd419b0f76","tid":140170,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實老人搭飛機有無得免費Upgrade頭等?</blockquote><br />\n睇下你係邊個囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9153c8f398c48904388b6652de85bec0df8ecb7","tid":140170,"uid":10320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:07:56.000Z","msg":"台仔戇撚鳩自己的造成， 冇得怨"},{"pid":"95e4beb70468ac02e75f9beea77559d2aec8cb16","tid":140170,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"其實有盤生意可做，叫&quot;道德保險&quot;"},{"pid":"2cc1845cf7e0ea9d647fabdf5a72aa966dc410fe","tid":140170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}